E scions scion beginning~
The Scions of Knowledge were not always as they now are. Originally a     
reclusive conclave of magi bent on the gathering of information of all     
sorts only for the bettering of themselves, the Scions were begun by a     
philosopher-mage named Kreousili upon the completion of the city of Kost.     
     
Peaceful in nature and few in number, the mages were recorded as taking     
but one violent action, which was their taking of the Glass Tower.     
~
